Package: seekit
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Plotting and Analysis Helpers for CyTOF and scRNA-seq
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("David", "Priest", email = "davidpriest898@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Plotting, save, and SingleCellExperiment/Seurat-handling helpers
    for high-dimensional single-cell analysis -- mass cytometry (CyTOF) and
    single-cell RNA-seq (CITE-seq / scRNA-seq). Functions historically vendored
    as per-project `R/<name>.R` copies; this package consolidates them into a
    single canonical source. Install per-project via renv to preserve
    reproducibility.
